{"tid":494047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大生沙田站跳軌遭輾斃 母親目擊傷心送院","createTime":"2017-12-09T07:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T09:16:42.000Z","uid":93642,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ace02165b2f118a935f44c14b4d3867809e0123e","tid":494047,"uid":93642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"上午10時50分，一名男子在沙田站北行月台墮軌，並遭一輛駛至列車輾過，重傷被困列車底，港鐵職員發現報警求助。救援人員接報到場，將男子救出移離路軌，但證實當場死亡。受事件影響，列車服務一度受阻，職員安排乘客轉搭其他列車；由於沙田站有多條路軌，列車服務很快回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱死者21歲，初步調查懷疑他趁列車埋站時跳落路軌，結果遭撞到。現場沒有遺書，據了解事主有情緒病。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆稱，沙田站職員目擊有乘客跌落二號月台(往羅湖)，即時按動緊急掣停止列車進出，當時正有一列車抵達此月台，車長即時煞停及通知控制中心，由控制中心報警。該列車上的乘客要落車，到對面月台轉乘另一列車。至11時20分，消防將該男子移離路軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=f7662d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&h=f4158f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNDS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔執唔執得齊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacc53b9b271f46be321b40420528438c744ad33","tid":494047,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"邊度有講佢係NDS?"},{"pid":"8a019675c3aeb18f1395a7a53ef2b0781f93953f","tid":494047,"uid":118120,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"【13:20更新】死者21歲，是中大學生，內地人，有情緒病紀錄"},{"pid":"0c55903b413c0f6214daf403af8dd8462acb044f","tid":494047,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"